text: Anastassiya Mirshina (born 21 March 1996) is a Kazakhstani female water polo player. She competed for the Kazakhstan women's national water polo team in the 2017 World Aquatics Championships, 2018 Asian Games, and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites== * Anastassiya+Mirshina zimbio * Anastassiya Mirshina of Kazakhstan competes xinhuanet Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani water polo players
